	   <tr><td colspan=2>I won the roll for these last night (WOOT!).&nbsp;&nbsp;Just need to get to ally now so I can get them...Hello Kael, here I come.<br><br>Since I see questions about where to get the gems, let me add this suggestion.  Our guild keeps a bank of gems on the officers' mules.  When we get quest gems, we turn them over so there's no scrambling to find the gems.  Makes it a lot easier.  <br><br>If you're high enough to get these quest pieces, pp should not be a problem for you, so giving up the gems to help other guild members out is the better thing to do.<br><br><br>Nestefus<br>Lvl 55 Evoker<br>House of Elder - Tarrew Marr<br>&nbsp;<br><br><br></td></tr>
