	   <tr><td colspan=2>Your guild rolls on HoT drops?<br><br>Wow.<br><br>Our guild goes on two different criteria...<br><br>a) What you have already<br>and<br>b) How much time and effort you put into the guild.<br><br>I don't think that's unreasonable. The guild is getting you the gear in HoT, they want to put it to the best use possible.<br><br>BPs and Robes are an exception. Those usually go by seniority due to the rareness.<br>&nbsp;<br>Branaddar Balefire<br>Wizard of the 59th Spire<br>&lt;Rendered Asylum&gt;<br>Tholuxe Paells</td></tr>
